{"tid":535914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港語學】承諾取消　卻不取消　翻譯系同學普通話能力優良　卻不合格","createTime":"2018-01-21T10:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T08:12:46.000Z","uid":47714,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6fa97b1c8b6cca4dbba6ed01f422de692ec28b","tid":535914,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/1658853600838025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F1658853600838025&d=AmyvZJfVCLEFjrm7gTaWZf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=12fc000a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/1658853600838025</a><br />\n<br />\n陳樂行：「 2016 年發起公投要求校方取消學生修讀普通話課程作為畢業要求，事件令校方增設普通話豁免試，當時校方話個考試主要係考核口頭能力同預期大部份同學會合格。<br />\n<br />\n有翻譯系同學指自己在班內的普通話能力良好，當日考普通話豁免試時，考官指其語氣不像考題設定的角色，該同學今日收到是不合格的結果。<br />\n<br />\n校方此舉是為難學生，欺騙同學和背信棄義。」"},{"pid":"6cb93b357b742a7381aee45b98ab819b1a6c0a72","tid":535914,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c737a431a6e1e774bfd8516eb88ae4e3ceb7a76","tid":535914,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考官指其語氣不像考題設定的角色，該同學今日收到是不合格的結果。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考官係支那人黎？"},{"pid":"c6a7fb7bdec1a1caa8b7c11cfa78d73e45614731","tid":535914,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T18:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a976ab2c790029913ce72fea8d3d38a53641ad18","tid":535914,"uid":77453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T18:23:52.000Z","msg":"外國藉既永久性居民都係當外語學生唔駛考<br />\n大把香港人都有 外國藉，有 bug 可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}